25
00:02:02,819 --> 00:02:04,220
This place...

26
00:02:04,659 --> 00:02:06,139
I feel like I've been here before.

27
00:02:08,019 --> 00:02:10,059
Maybe it was in that illusion.

28
00:02:13,780 --> 00:02:14,618
Who's there?

29
00:02:14,619 --> 00:02:15,779
Why are you sneaking around?

30
00:02:18,019 --> 00:02:18,859
Zhilou?

31
00:02:18,860 --> 00:02:19,980
Uncle Qingyun?

32
00:02:21,019 --> 00:02:21,979
I finally found you.

33
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:23,099
Where did you go?

34
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:24,058
Are you alright?

35
00:02:24,059 --> 00:02:25,259
Did you get hurt?

36
00:02:25,260 --> 00:02:26,259
I'm fine.

37
00:02:26,260 --> 00:02:27,659
Patrols are everywhere.

38
00:02:27,660 --> 00:02:29,099
I just saw a group

39
00:02:29,100 --> 00:02:30,099
forcing a bunch of girls

40
00:02:30,100 --> 00:02:31,178
onto a carriage.

41
00:02:31,179 --> 00:02:32,618
Their cries sounded awful.

42
00:02:32,619 --> 00:02:34,420
Should we help them?

43
00:02:34,820 --> 00:02:36,659
Did they head
toward the cave in the back?

44
00:02:36,940 --> 00:02:37,778
I heard

45
00:02:37,779 --> 00:02:40,339
they were
taking some mountain path to Wujing.

46
00:02:40,499 --> 00:02:41,779
Wujing?

47
00:02:41,899 --> 00:02:43,219
What's going on?

48
00:02:43,899 --> 00:02:44,859
Zhilou,

49
00:02:44,860 --> 00:02:46,139
something's off.

50
00:02:46,140 --> 00:02:47,460
We need to split up.

51
00:02:47,660 --> 00:02:48,659
Fei Yuan, Bai Lu,

52
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:50,738
go with my uncle and stop that carriage.

53
00:02:50,739 --> 00:02:52,860
I'll check the cave with Chu Moshang.

54
00:02:53,899 --> 00:02:54,699
Zhilou,

55
00:02:54,700 --> 00:02:55,819
that cave is dangerous.

56
00:02:55,820 --> 00:02:57,219
I won't allow you to go.

57
00:02:57,220 --> 00:02:58,338
Uncle Qingyun,

58
00:02:58,339 --> 00:03:00,338
I'm not that useless girl I used to be.

59
00:03:00,339 --> 00:03:01,460
Don't worry.

60
00:03:01,619 --> 00:03:02,980
I'll keep her safe.

61
00:03:17,220 --> 00:03:19,898
Even through the barrier,
I can feel the chill coming from inside.

62
00:03:19,899 --> 00:03:21,700
Looks like this is the Frigid Zone.

63
00:03:22,380 --> 00:03:23,499
Feng Zhilou,

64
00:03:23,579 --> 00:03:25,980
your body can't stand it.

65
00:03:27,380 --> 00:03:30,260
We're already at the entrance,
and you're trying to stop me?

66
00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:31,778
I know

67
00:03:31,779 --> 00:03:34,339
you've always wanted
to fight alongside the Dragons.

